## CogniRepo Tool Routing

Project: {project_name}
Data: {project_path}/.cognirepo/

BEFORE reading any file >100 lines:   use mcp_{project_name}_context_pack first.
BEFORE searching for a function:      use mcp_{project_name}_lookup_symbol first.
BEFORE tracing callers:               use mcp_{project_name}_who_calls first.
AFTER a non-trivial decision:         use mcp_{project_name}_store_memory to record it.

If context_pack returns no_confident_match → fall back to file read.
If who_calls returns empty → the fallback field will contain string-literal hits.

For file-specific context (Cursor file mode):
  use context_pack(file="path/to/file.py") to get all indexed symbols for a file.
